query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('alamofire',
'amazon-cognito',
'classloader',
'complexity-theory',
'database-performance',
'dependency-properties',
'ejb-3.0',
'jhipster',
'nsfetchedresultscontroller',
'positioning',
'rcpp',
'refresh',
'session-cookies',
'string-formatting',
'symfony-1.4');
